Hydras:::

"All Fuctional predacons stay alert..."said sharply Hydras while he headed 
towards the the base"Cyclonus and Tarantulus, if you are with slight 
scrachers... WORK in that place, I wanted it undetectable and secure; this 
is a temporal refuge, but we will remain there a while..."said Hydras while 
he typed an encoded message to his 'Tutor' "I'm interested in your offer, my 
tutor, for the blank protophorm and a base... say your price..."

-----Original Message----- 
From: Super Cyclonus
Sent: Friday, May 06, 2011 11:15 AM
To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: Hydras and Predacons

There is a slight pause and then an answer comes from Sky Shadow, the
Fuzor leader, "Sir, most of the Predacons are in the recharge
chambers, preparing themselves for the next glorious battle."

Tarantulus also chimed in over the radio, "This uh base, if you call
it that, is going to need alot of work to get it back up and running
again."

Cyclonus, Scourge, Deepstryke, and a few sweeps landed near Hydras as
they followed him in. Most of them also looked damaged, several of
them leaking lubracant.

"Sir, we all will need repairs to get us all back up to fighting
strength." Cyclonus said.

Scourge just grunted as he looked over the group, but there were a few
wounds on him as well.

Inferno, that Hydras was still carrying looked to be in bad sape, he
was basically in stassis lock, his wounds having over come him on the
trip home.

(TAG)

Preston
